Package antlr

Class SimpleCBaseVisitor<T>

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
antlr.SimpleCBaseVisitor<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
SimpleCVisitor<T>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
IRBuilder, SimpleCPrinter
public class SimpleCBaseVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T> implements SimpleCVisitor<T>
This class provides an empty implementation of SimpleCVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
